---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Week 8: 力のモーメント">
  <h1>Week 8: 力のモーメント</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">回転させる力の正体！</p>

  <h2>🎯 今日の目標</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>力のモーメント（トルク）を計算できる</li>
    <li>うでの長さを正しく求められる</li>
    <li>モーメントのつり合い条件を使える</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>力のモーメントとは</h2>

  <div class="highlight-box">
    <strong>🚪 なぜドアは取っ手を押すと開きやすい？</strong><br/>
    蝶番（支点）から遠いほど、小さい力で回転させられる！
  </div>

  <div class="formula-box">
    <span class="big-formula">M = F × d</span>
    <p>モーメント = 力 × うでの長さ</p>
  </div>

  <table>
    <tr><th>記号</th><th>意味</th><th>単位</th></tr>
    <tr><td>M</td><td>力のモーメント</td><td>N·m</td></tr>
    <tr><td>F</td><td>力の大きさ</td><td>N</td></tr>
    <tr><td>d</td><td>うでの長さ</td><td>m</td></tr>
  </table>

  <h3>うでの長さとは</h3>
  <div class="highlight-box">
    回転軸（支点）から力の <strong>作用線</strong> までの <strong>垂直距離</strong>
  </div>

  <h3>モーメントの符号</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>反時計回り：＋（正）</strong></li>
    <li><strong>時計回り：−（負）</strong></li>
  </ul>

  <h2>🎮 シーソーバランス</h2>
  <div class="animation-container">
    <div id="seesaw-sim">
      <div class="seesaw-display">
        <div class="seesaw-board" id="seesaw-board">
          <div class="weight left-weight">🏋️ <span id="left-w">20</span>kg</div>
          <div class="fulcrum">△</div>
          <div class="weight right-weight">🏋️ <span id="right-w">10</span>kg</div>
        </div>
        <div class="scale">
          <span>-5</span><span>-4</span><span>-3</span><span>-2</span><span>-1</span>
          <span>0</span>
          <span>1</span><span>2</span><span>3</span><span>4</span><span>5</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="seesaw-controls">
        <div>
          <label>左の重さ: <input type="number" id="left-mass" value="20" min="1" max="50" /> kg</label>
          <label>左の位置: <input type="number" id="left-pos" value="-3" min="-5" max="-1" /> m</label>
        </div>
        <div>
          <label>右の重さ: <input type="number" id="right-mass" value="10" min="1" max="50" /> kg</label>
          <label>右の位置: <input type="number" id="right-pos" value="3" min="1" max="5" /> m</label>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="seesaw-calc">
        <p>左のモーメント: <span id="left-m">60</span> N·m（反時計回り）</p>
        <p>右のモーメント: <span id="right-m">30</span> N·m（時計回り）</p>
        <p id="balance-status">⚠️ 左に傾く！</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>剛体のつり合い条件</h2>

  <div class="highlight-box">
    剛体が静止するには、<strong>2つの条件</strong> が必要！
  </div>

  <div class="formula-box">
    <p><strong>条件1：力のつり合い</strong></p>
    <span class="big-formula">ΣFx = 0, ΣFy = 0</span>
    <p><strong>条件2：モーメントのつり合い</strong></p>
    <span class="big-formula">ΣM = 0</span>
  </div>

  <h2>例題</h2>

  <div class="example">
    <h4>例題1：てこ</h4>
    <p><strong>問題：</strong>支点から左2mに30N、右xmに20N。つり合うxは？</p>
    <p><strong>解答：</strong></p>
    <p>左のモーメント（反時計）= 右のモーメント（時計）</p>
    <p>30 × 2 = 20 × x</p>
    <p>x = 60 / 20 = <strong>3 m</strong></p>
  </div>

  <div class="example">
    <h4>例題2：棒を支える</h4>
    <p><strong>問題：</strong>長さ10m、重さ8Nの一様な棒。端Aから3mに4Nの力。両端A,Bの反力は？</p>
    <p><strong>解答：</strong></p>
    <p>Aまわりのモーメント：</p>
    <p>RB × 10 = 8 × 5 + 4 × 3 = 40 + 12 = 52</p>
    <p>RB = <strong>5.2 N</strong></p>
    <p>力のつり合い：RA + RB = 8 + 4 = 12</p>
    <p>RA = 12 - 5.2 = <strong>6.8 N</strong></p>
  </div>

  <h2>練習問題</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>問題</th><th>解答</th></tr>
    <tr>
      <td>① 支点から2mで50Nの力を加える。モーメントは？</td>
      <td><details><summary>答え</summary>M = 50 × 2 = 100 N·m</details></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>② 左3mに40N、右にxmに60N。つり合うxは？</td>
      <td><details><summary>答え</summary>40×3 = 60×x → x = 2 m</details></td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <h2>📝 今日のポイント</h2>
  <div class="highlight-box">
    <ul>
      <li>✓ モーメント：<strong>M = Fd</strong>（回転させる能力）</li>
      <li>✓ うでの長さ：支点から作用線への垂直距離</li>
      <li>✓ つり合い：<strong>ΣM = 0</strong></li>
      <li>✓ 支点の選び方で計算が楽になる！</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="nav-buttons">
    <a href="/physics-basic/weeks/week07/" class="nav-btn secondary">← Week 7</a>
    <a href="/physics-basic/weeks/week09/" class="nav-btn">Week 9 へ →</a>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .subtitle { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: -0.5rem; }
  .formula-box { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff, #dbeafe); border: 2px solid var(--primary); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  .big-formula { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--primary-dark); display: block; margin: 0.5rem 0; }
  #seesaw-sim { padding: 1rem; }
  .seesaw-display { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .seesaw-board { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; padding: 0 2rem; height: 60px; background: linear-gradient(to right, #fef3c7, #fde68a); border-radius: 4px; transition: transform 0.3s; position: relative; }
  .weight { font-size: 1.2rem; }
  .fulcrum { position: absolute; left: 50%; bottom: -20px; transform: translateX(-50%); font-size: 1.5rem; }
  .scale { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0 1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748b; }
  .seesaw-controls { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin: 1rem 0; }
  .seesaw-controls label { display: block; margin: 0.25rem 0; }
  .seesaw-controls input { width: 60px; padding: 0.25rem; }
  .seesaw-calc { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; }
  .seesaw-calc p { margin: 0; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; background: #f1f5f9; border-radius: 4px; }
  #balance-status { font-weight: bold; }
  details summary { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; }
</style>

<script>
  const leftMass = document.getElementById('left-mass') as HTMLInputElement;
  const leftPos = document.getElementById('left-pos') as HTMLInputElement;
  const rightMass = document.getElementById('right-mass') as HTMLInputElement;
  const rightPos = document.getElementById('right-pos') as HTMLInputElement;
  const leftW = document.getElementById('left-w');
  const rightW = document.getElementById('right-w');
  const leftM = document.getElementById('left-m');
  const rightM = document.getElementById('right-m');
  const status = document.getElementById('balance-status');
  const board = document.getElementById('seesaw-board');

  function update() {
    const mL = parseInt(leftMass?.value || '20');
    const pL = Math.abs(parseInt(leftPos?.value || '3'));
    const mR = parseInt(rightMass?.value || '10');
    const pR = parseInt(rightPos?.value || '3');

    const momentL = mL * 10 * pL;
    const momentR = mR * 10 * pR;

    if (leftW) leftW.textContent = mL.toString();
    if (rightW) rightW.textContent = mR.toString();
    if (leftM) leftM.textContent = momentL.toString();
    if (rightM) rightM.textContent = momentR.toString();

    const diff = momentL - momentR;
    const angle = Math.max(-15, Math.min(15, diff / 20));
    
    if (board) board.style.transform = `rotate(${-angle}deg)`;
    
    if (status) {
      if (Math.abs(diff) < 5) {
        status.textContent = '✅ バランス！Perfect!';
        status.style.color = '#22c55e';
      } else if (diff > 0) {
        status.textContent = '⚠️ 左に傾く！';
        status.style.color = '#f59e0b';
      } else {
        status.textContent = '⚠️ 右に傾く！';
        status.style.color = '#f59e0b';
      }
    }
  }

  [leftMass, leftPos, rightMass, rightPos].forEach(el => el?.addEventListener('input', update));
  update();
</script>
